    • Constructor Detail

      • ToClientPacket

        public ToClientPacket(int clientId,
                      String serverCMD,
                      String outputLine)
        The object is a data storage of an string of data, a timestamp made on creation on the object and the clientId. It is used to save messages that are outbound towards a client.
        Parameters:
        clientId - The clientId number this package should go to
        serverCMD - The string containing the type of command the server sends
        outputLine - The string containing the command payload.
